    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.63.26_0001a" />
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        Lincoln Neb.
                        58505<sic>68505</sic>
                        7-23-'72
                    </dateline>
                    
                    <salute>Dear Lucile:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>Simon &amp; Shuster<sic>Schuster</sic> are preparing a paper-back edition of <hi rend="underline">When the Tree Flowered</hi>. They want extracts of book reviews. I believe you have <del/>them. American and British reviews. Will you look into this and send the best you can f<del/><add>ind</add>, please!
                
                    <note type="authorial">(over)</note>
                    
                    <pb facs="nei.j4c.63.26_0001b"/>
                    <fw type="authorial">-2-</fw>
                    
                    You could mail <del>direct</del> direct to &#8212;
                    <address>
                        <addrLine><del>Mr Bernard</del></addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Mr. Bernard Shir-Cliff,</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>c/o Simon &amp; Shuster<sic>Schuster</sic>,</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Rockefeller Center</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>630 Fifth Ave.,</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>New York, N.Y 1002<unclear/></addrLine>
                    </address>
                </p>
                
                <p>I think it would be well for him to know about your biography!! If you write him, us<unclear/> opportunity.</p>
                
                    <note type="authorial">(Inside</note>
                
                    <fw type="curatorial">26</fw>
                
                <note>
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>Shir-Cliff</addrLine>
                        <addrLine><hi rend="italics"><hi rend="caps">SIMON &amp; SCHUSTER, INC.</hi></hi></addrLine>
                        <addrLine><hi rend="italics">Rockefeller Center</hi></addrLine>
                        <addrLine><hi rend="italics">630 Fifth Avenue</hi></addrLine>
                        <addrLine><hi rend="italics">New York, N.Y. 10020</hi></addrLine>
                    </address>
                </note>
                
                    <pb facs="nei.j4c.63.26_0002"/>
                    <fw type="authorial">-3-</fw>
                
                <p>Excuse my bad writing.</p>
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
